{"id": "1197461115056177153", "channel_id": "1197139130182803517", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168245675419508766", "author_name": "arielsred", "author_bot": false, "content": "有15個造物不在榜上呢~\n增值系列：7個\n即刻系列：6個 (除了行道之骸)，如圖示。\n除了這兩系列之外，還少了護佑系列的「普尼特晨報」和節律系列的「蠱惑風鈴」，這兩個WIKI上有。\n另外，有三個造物重複上榜了：甜蜜墨水、三棱鏡、超弦懷錶。", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T08:42:57.581000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1197461114875813948", "filename": "2e69f9997747d3e9.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 241760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197139130182803517/1197461114875813948/2e69f9997747d3e9.png?ex=69cb8911&is=69ca3791&hm=69e3b1bf50c437e8ec0e8794f59758bacb1cda7ee07c87b60b70c5cc15cc7be9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197139130182803517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜造物T度榜", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
