{"id": "1197566928072495306", "channel_id": "1197139130182803517", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168245675419508766", "author_name": "arielsred", "author_bot": false, "content": "期待大佬的後續攻略呢！！\n這裡先幫忙整理了一下，\n造物總共有19個系列，一個系列有7個\n19*7=133，目前共有133個造物\n(應該吧？還是有遺漏掉的系列，歡迎更正喔~）", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T15:43:25.370000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T15:52:02.675000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197566927401402388", "filename": "67b389ec8e3613d2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 7059497, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197139130182803517/1197566927401402388/67b389ec8e3613d2.jpg?ex=69cbeb9d&is=69ca9a1d&hm=eb9b663cea216e1e8d2b6d3df42f9c3537625277262c466ec23c34ac40326ea2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197139130182803517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜造物T度榜", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
