{"id": "1197356814426193972", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 虚弱\n留存效果类别，此类症状卡若在回合结束后留存在手中，会对玩家造成负面影响。\n一般会在队伍内缺少虚弱刻印的时候考虑打出，能够稳定1费上虚弱比起朵儿的2费虚弱是一个优点。但是留存效果也同样较为致命，减少25%输出在关键时刻是十分致命的。\n\n笔者评分：3️⃣不功不过", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:48:30.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:07:26.933000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 21}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197356814199697419", "filename": "IMG_3676.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 218100, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197356814199697419/IMG_3676.png?ex=69cbd0ae&is=69ca7f2e&hm=370b3e0eba37cb11b03ca1389c5544195cee6c3303bc86f675942a8c6860f2de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197356996442210304", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 崩溃\n留存效果类别，此类症状卡若在回合结束后留存在手中，会对玩家造成负面影响。\n隐藏效果其实是在夫人队中可以不占空间上易伤。值得一提的是这张症状卡的效果并不是对称的，在手中留存时给玩家的负面效果是脆弱而不是易伤，两者的致命性差距还是十分大的。\n\n笔者评分：2️⃣好像能用", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:49:13.769000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:08:42.643000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 23}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197356996182155325", "filename": "IMG_3689.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 219283, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197356996182155325/IMG_3689.png?ex=69cbd0d9&is=69ca7f59&hm=670f575a80e7201837b9d3e048ab8fce469d5b5538add935fae4f26997121d4c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197357198746071142", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 盲从\n留存效果类别，此类症状卡若在回合结束后留存在手中，会对玩家造成负面影响。\n若卡组中没有能够处理手中牌的角色稍为致命，在手中放几个回合你就会发现你的卡组被垃圾填满了。而换来的25%暴击率也是高风险高回报了。\n\n笔者评分：1️⃣正面造物", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:50:02.002000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:08:52.234000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197357198557331586", "filename": "IMG_3687.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 168531, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197357198557331586/IMG_3687.png?ex=69cbd109&is=69ca7f89&hm=4616f81673a19034b8e086336a515c3641683bb61b32ee19655ebd9a0f9308dd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197357487607783554", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 颓废\n抽中触发类别，此类症状在任意时候被抽到都会触发负面效果。\n噔 噔 咚 \n不接受反驳，这就是笔者认为最恶心的症状卡。不知有多少次自己刚准备开大，然后因为抽到这张症状被迫重开。唯一的神，症状颓废。\n\n笔者评分：5️⃣死也不会拿", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:51:10.872000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:08:25.081000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 30}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197357487423225888", "filename": "IMG_3686.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160078, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197357487423225888/IMG_3686.png?ex=69cbd14e&is=69ca7fce&hm=1ade5e085992c0db87b0737aef0f668099be8b3eba4c343378129286997e9b01&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
