{"id": "1197357859395080344", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 呓语\n污染牌库类别，此类症状在打出后会将一份复制洗入牌库。\n一费抽二本身其实是合格的，但是污染牌库却和过牌产生了冲突，较为尴尬的一张牌。\n\n笔者评价：4️⃣拿了会很难受", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:52:39.513000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:09:37.979000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 18}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197357859223117926", "filename": "IMG_3688.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 196270, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197357859223117926/IMG_3688.png?ex=69cbd1a7&is=69ca8027&hm=cc92164bc041d62bd535242c3d2ef8037aa58ed6f67a623af2c55e208a20451f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197357993960931418", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 臆想\n污染牌库类别，此类症状在打出后会将一份复制洗入牌库。\n零费产一费在关键时刻会十分有用，其负面效果和同等类别的烧血产费相比要优秀不少。\n\n笔者评价：3️⃣不功不过", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:53:11.596000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:09:54.972000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 16}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197357993738641510", "filename": "IMG_3690.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 258783, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197357993738641510/IMG_3690.png?ex=69cbd1c7&is=69ca8047&hm=af0e5ee1d5d480c7d643a13489f7f43be98d1d0f97121b8900f486a8fed5478f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197358194603868310", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 兴奋\n下回合生效类别，此类症状若满足一定条件会在下回合产生效果。\n不能打出是非常致命的一点，而其需要剩余算力的需求在绝大多数情况都要求玩家进行有牌不能打的操作。这两点导致其在同类别的多疑比较下较为尴尬。\n\n笔者评价：4️⃣拿了会很难受", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:53:59.433000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:10:11.641000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 21}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197358194327031838", "filename": "IMG_3685.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 166037, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197358194327031838/IMG_3685.png?ex=69cbd1f7&is=69ca8077&hm=1fc944375b940e399216cba9471636d343b91bd4b204adc5547ad5ad62951b73&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197358314275753994", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 多疑\n下回合生效类别，此类症状若满足一定条件会在下回合产生效果。\n适合费用比例较高的一些卡组。说是比另一张好些但其实也没有好到哪里去。少于三张的出牌任务比起算力要稍微好做一些，但大多数情况还是要刻意去完成的。\n\n笔者评价：3️⃣不功不过", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:54:27.965000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:10:36.032000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197358314045059112", "filename": "IMG_3681.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175655, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197358314045059112/IMG_3681.png?ex=69cbd213&is=69ca8093&hm=5994d02e38d28c9bbcd8e89a110bb2db1c7c3af967dd35861c6547da6ce3b500&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197358440830468156", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "439267709281239040", "author_name": "chros0110", "author_bot": false, "content": "+\n+\n+\n症状 谵妄\n最特殊的一张症状卡，三费的锁链一击，额外的一张断头你喜欢吗？\n根据以后的新角色评价会变化很多的一张特殊症状，较为适合整体卡组卡牌均十分优质的卡组。其缺点有二：一为保留的特性，导致这张牌会一直占手牌上限，二为打击和防御永远都会存在，导致这张牌总会有不尽人意的时候。\n\n笔者评价：2️⃣好像有用", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T01:54:58.138000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T02:10:59.953000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}, {"emoji": "3️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "5️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 18}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197358440645927012", "filename": "IMG_3668.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 60032, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197355169105592390/1197358440645927012/IMG_3668.png?ex=69cbd232&is=69ca80b2&hm=81c4f7d35fbdf0b13ba367b359a0416419a3ebabcf0b003ec7a648d394fbc7d7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1197451571823394900", "channel_id": "1197355169105592390", "type": 0, "author_id": "1183697008435920929", "author_name": "sphinxneko", "author_bot": false, "content": "怎么说呢，我体感的情况下，只要症状卡负面不会暴毙，基本都有点用，因为大多数情况下症状卡是和造物一起选的，所以像臆想，兴奋这种如果和造物绑定，直接无脑选，战斗中不用就行了🥺", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T08:05:02.297000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197355169105592390", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【图鉴整合】症状卡投票恶心程度评分贴", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
